(43, 19, 31, 43, 19, 42, 42, NULL, 'Connection of Preparation Day', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of the preparation day for the Jews. The first mentions the preparation for the sabbath, while the second refers to Jesus being laid in the sepulchre because of this preparation.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
