(43, 19, 35, 62, 1, 1, 3, 'bare record, and his record is true', 'Witness and Belief Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of witnessing and truth. Both passages emphasize the importance of firsthand experience in bearing witness to Jesus, which is essential for belief and fellowship.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
